HAPI FHIR JPA Server Starter
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Source:    https://github.com/hapifhir/hapi-fhir-jpaserver-starter
Version:   8.8.0
Licence:   Apache License, Version 2.0
           https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

The fhir-server module is derived from the HAPI FHIR JPA Server Starter.
The following files were modified from the original:

  - src/main/java/ca/uhn/fhir/jpa/starter/util/JpaHibernatePropertiesProvider.java
    Change: Added Spring Environment injection to resolve Hibernate dialect
    from spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect before falling back to
    JDBC connection-based auto-detection. This prevents dialect detection
    from opening a connection to a fallback embedded H2 datasource when
    the primary datasource is PostgreSQL.

  - src/main/java/ca/uhn/fhir/jpa/starter/common/FhirServerConfigCommon.java
    Change: Updated jpaStarterDialectProvider bean method to pass Spring
    Environment to JpaHibernatePropertiesProvider constructor.

  - src/main/resources/application.yaml
    Change: Updated spring.application.name and spring.datasource.url
    for this platform's configuration.

